data.description: Beautiful daylight walkout rancher backing up to the greenbelt. 6 bedrooms, 4 FULL bathrooms. Giant main floor master suite w/ huge walk-in shower and a second master suite w/ walk-in closet downstairs.  Great room concept with cathedral ceilings, hardwood floors, solid wood doors, and a 3 car garage. Territorial views from the back deck and lower patio.
